06/http://www.newyorker.com/critics/books/articles/060807crbo_books Nick Mount on Samuel Beckett's ''Waiting For Godot''. Video lecture. University of Toronto.]. Retrieved 2010-08-24\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20121112095234/http://cle.ens-lyon.fr/anglais/dystopia-in-the-plays-of-samuel-beckett-br-purgatory-in-play-166882.kjsp?RH=CDL_ANG000000 Dystopia in the plays of Samuel Beckett: Purgatory in ''Play'' (Eleanor Bryce)]. Retrieved 2012-10-02\n* [https://digital.ucd.ie/view/ivrla:6352 The Beckett Country Collection. A UCD Digital Library Collection] \n* [https://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/literature/laureates/1969/beckett-bio.html Nobel profile]\n* {{isfdb name|id=20243|name=Samuel Beckett}}\n* {{NPG name}}\n* [[BBC Radio 4]] programme on Samuel Beckett with James Knowlson: [http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00wqbjq listen online]\n* [http://census.nationalarchives.ie/pages/1911/Dublin/Ballybrack/Kerrymount/96765/ The Beckett family in the 1911 Census of Ireland]\n\n{{Samuel Beckett}}\n{{Nobel Prize in Literature Laureates 1951-1975}}\n{{Irish poetry}}\n{{Portal bar|Literature|Biography}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Beckett, Samuel}}\n[[Category:Samuel Beckett| ]]\n[[Category:1906 births]]\n[[Category:1989 deaths]]\n[[Category:Academics of Trinity College Dublin]]\n[[Category:Analysands of Wilfred Bion]]\n[[Category:Anti-natalists]]\n[[Category:Burials at Montparnasse Cemetery]]\n[[Category:Deaths from emphysema]]\n[[Category:Dublin University cricketers]]\n[[Category:\u00c9cole Normale Sup\u00e9rieure faculty]]\n[[Category:Exophonic writers]]\n[[Category:Fellows of the American Academy of Arts and Sciences]]\n[[Category:French Resistance members]]\n[[Category:Irish agnostics]]\n[[Category:Irish artists]]\n[[Category:Irish cricketers]]\n[[Category:Irish expatriates in France]]\n[[Category:Irish male dramatists and playwrights]]\n[[Category:Irish male novelists]]\n[[Category:Irish male short story writers]]\n[[Category:Irish short story writer